For the following exercises, use the sets provided to apply the “AND” or “OR” operation as indicated to find the resulting set.

U = { a , b , c , … , z } U = \{ a,b,c, \ldots ,z\}, S = { s , a , m , p , l , e } S = \{ s,a,m,p,l,e\}, M = { m , a , p } M = \{ m,a,p\}, L = { l , a , m , p } L = \{ l,a,m,p\}, D = { d , o , g } D = \{ d,o,g\}, and P = { p , l , o , t } P = \{ p,l,o,t\}.
